= Test Day

== What to Bring

- Valid government-issued ID (passport recommended)
- Confirmation email/number
- Nothing else (lockers provided)

== What's Provided

- Scratch paper/whiteboard and markers
- Noise-canceling headphones (optional)
- Locker for personal items

